  "text": "Methotrexate. Methotrexate is an antimetabolite that prevents the conversion of bihydrofolic acid to tetrahydrofolic acid. Although the authors of a few small open studies involving methotrexate have reported a potential effect in AS, a metaanalysis performed by Chen and Liu [CITATION_1] failed to reveal that it had any role. No placebo-controlled studies have been performed to date.",
